text: Sigmaringendorf is a municipality in Sigmaringen in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. In Sigmaringendorf the small river Lauchert flows into the Danube. It has an open-air-theatre called Waldbühne Sigmaringendorf. It has two localities are Sigmaringendorf and Laucherthal. The current mayor of Sigmaringendorf is Phillip Schwaiger since 2017. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Sigmaringen (district)
